high_descs: Walk forward then turn right head to the table
Pick up the glass on the table
Turn left then head to the fridge
Open the fridge then put in and out the glass then close the fridge
Turn right then head to the table
Put the glass on the table in front of the potato
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled glass on the table

high_descs: Cross the room and face the wood table with various items on it.
Pick the glass up from the table.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Put the glass in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick the glass up again and shut the door.
Turn around and face the wood table.
Put the glass down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the brown table in the corner of the room.
Pick up the glass on the round table to the left of the gray plate.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the glass for a moment in the refrigerator, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the brown table.
Place the glass on the brown table to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Chill a drinking glass in the refrigerator and put it on the brown table.
